name: Aaron Hinton
text: Just left there at 2:30 on 5/24.  Horrible service. Asked a simple question and the food.  The woman and the man both working there rude hateful people.  I tried to be polite despite their attitudes and it didn’t help.  Never go there again. Don’t bother. Not to mention the pizza tasted like it’s been there all day

name: Mark Davis
text: Man great pizza for the money, mouth watering joy.

name: Richard Patrick
text: Good pizza. Reminds me of New York.
